  "title": "别再迷信大模型！吴恩达亲授 AI 秘籍：小模型+边缘计算=财富密码",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652640343&idx=3&sn=6ba0cb14c56800971649ab237b52ca59",
  "date": "2025-10-30 04:50:00",
